From: ruyue <ruyueee@outlook.com>
Date: Mon, 13 Apr 2026 20:28:49 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 5/6] Add Pop-Up View support

squashe:
- SDK: Port Pop-Up View feature from Nothing OS 2
- Base: Add Pop-Up View support with adaptations for 16-qpr0
- Fix: Avoid InputChannel of Gesture Monitor being disposed

Ruyue:
- Adapt to Android16 qpr2
- Add dock window mode
- Add smooth anim
- remove pinned window overlayview

